quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  107,1,Have you seen the one who denies the Day of Judgment
  107,2,He it is who drives away the orphan with harshness
  107,3,and does not encourage the feeding of the poor
  107,4,So woe to those who offer Salah (prayers)
  107,5,but are neglectful of their Salah (offer Prayers but disregard the very purpose of establishing Salah - to have the fear of Allah and be mindful to the needs of other people)
  107,6,those who make a show of piety
  107,7,and refuse to share the necessities of life